 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking water is the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing chess is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking water##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
