.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, ship, subway, train
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person driving the subway is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person driving the train is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Transport         | train | subway | ship | roller  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

